' Bouncy ball demo

Bob Off : Sprite Off : Rainbow Del
Screen 0
Screen Open 0,720,576,16777216,Hires+Laced
Load Iff "resources/starfield.jpg",0
Load "resources/sprites", 1


AMAL Channel 1
bouncy ball demo

Let X=Z(500)+20; Let Y=Z(240)+20;
Let A=6;

Let R0=Z(40)-20; Let R1=Z(40)-20;

Loop:
	Pause;
	
add the x and y speed values
to our x and y positions
	Let X = X + R0;
	Let Y = Y + R1;
	
add some gravity to the equation
	Let R1 = R1 + 2;

bounce if hit the floor or ceiling
	If Y<20 Jump Bounce
	If Y>480 Jump Bounce
    
shim if hit the wall
	If X<20 Jump Shim
	If X>600 Jump Shim    
Jump Loop


Bounce:
	Let R1 = 0 - R1;
	Let Y = Y + R1;
	Let R1 = R1 * 90;
	Let R1 = R1 / 100;
Jump Loop

Shim:
	Let R0 = 0 - R0;
	Let X = X + R0;
Jump Loop

